Subject: Re: [T2] Bus oil Low pressure Help

Even on my type one engines I used either 40 or 50 weight valvoline race 
oil.  Dont leave that in for winter though.  I always went synthetic in 
winter because of our erratic climate here.  Same as mentioned in 
another thread check the sender and see if oil is coming out around the 
contact.
jimt
